DarkMouse::

She looked at Destructor, still shaking a little as she walked with 
him,"He tried to kill me in the woods when him and that other bot 
found Inferno talking. I don't understand why he won't believe me. I 
have no reason to hide anything. I have nothing to hide."  She didn't 
know that he knew about her mech fluid.
